sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User
    participant Customer as Customer Agent :10100
    participant Registry as Registry :10000
    participant Law as Law Agent :10101
    participant Tax as Tax Agent :10102
    participant Compliance as Compliance Agent :10103
    participant LLM as OpenRouter LLM

    Note over Customer,Tax: trace_id=c44fc1bb-2db0-499e-bd6e-567478e57e25
    User->>Customer: A2A send_message(question)
    Customer->>LLM: Decide whether to delegate
    LLM-->>Customer: Call delegate_to_legal_agent
    Customer->>Registry: discover("legal_question")
    Registry-->>Customer: law-agent endpoint
    Customer->>Law: A2A send_message(question, trace_id, depth=1)
    Law->>LLM: Analyze law and route specialists
    LLM-->>Law: needs_tax=True, needs_compliance=False
    Law->>Registry: discover("tax_question")
    Registry-->>Law: tax-agent endpoint
    Law->>Tax: A2A send_message(question, trace_id, depth=2)
    Tax->>LLM: Tax specialist analysis
    LLM-->>Tax: Tax answer
    Tax-->>Law: Tax analysis artifact
    Law->>LLM: Aggregate law + tax analysis
    LLM-->>Law: Final legal response
    Law-->>Customer: Legal specialist response
    Customer->>LLM: Format final user response
    LLM-->>Customer: Final answer
    Customer-->>User: A2A response

    Note over Law,Tax: Dynamic discovery test: when Tax Agent was stopped, Registry still returned tax-agent endpoint, but Law Agent failed with httpx.ConnectError and returned a fallback response.
